{"tid":1170361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"諾華藥廠售價210萬美元新藥獲准銷售 全球最貴","createTime":"2019-05-25T02:57:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T03:25:08.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"afd0b0806c6690816b926afc6729dd3bbde1e0cd","tid":1170361,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T02:57:59.000Z","msg":"美國聯邦食品及藥物管理局(FDA)批准瑞士諾華藥廠(Novartis)新藥Zolgensma的銷售，Zolgensma成為全球售價最昂貴的藥物，售價高達210萬美元(1638萬港元)。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nZolgensma是以基因治療方式應對脊髓肌肉萎縮症 (spinal muscular atrophy)的一次性藥物，被指可以在初生嬰兒被確診有上述疾病時提供救治，及時救治以避免死亡的新樂。<br />\n<br />\n諾華曾表示，Zolgensma定價將介乎150萬至500萬美元。該公司稱，210萬美元是整個療程的總成本，病人分五年進行治療，即每年開支為42.5萬美元。該公司將與保險公司協商，如何協助病人成功進行為期五年的治療及支付費用。<br />\n<br />\n專門評估藥物價值的The Institute for Clinical and Economic Review認為，Zolgensma估值應為150萬美元，所以現時售價是高於估值上限水平。<br />\n<br />\n病人現時使用Biogen的Spinraza應對上述病症，Spinraza首年成本為75萬美元，其後每年為37.5萬美元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2146585\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2146585&d=QgRa2nBc7vcC6sJiZdE62PSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=e6f565d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2146585</a>"},{"pid":"e6ceaeff7c2ad54e50558cf000a7a7fca45a6e6f","tid":1170361,"uid":48531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T02:59:16.000Z","msg":"窮人真係唔好病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4e108ea3ff421f030e2eb610cb3025b0536feec","tid":1170361,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T03:01:19.000Z","msg":"有冇人解釋下點解食藥可以改到基因？"},{"pid":"0a7fb85598631c308f50525ccf494a99903cee8a","tid":1170361,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T03:03:15.000Z","msg":"食藥都係有錢佬權利 成日知足常樂掛口邊班公屋窮撚真係情何以堪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a87c35cac37da7d9b230f59097c02c56182adbd4","tid":1170361,"uid":36134,"like":2,"dis